# Bun

Usamos **bun** para todo:

- Package manager (`bun install`, `bun add`)
- Test runner (`bun test`)
- Runtime (`bun run`)

```bash
# ✅ CORRECTO
bun install
bun add zod
bun test
bun run build

# ❌ INCORRECTO
npm install
yarn add zod
jest
npx tsc
```
